{"tid":1207481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線報左，建制派坐住一部白色既28 座離開中區警署","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T08:22:10.000Z","uid":242724,"like":274,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":134,"replies":[{"pid":"10edf9cc2b7906598f02e6c0d538c17d43df00d5","tid":1207481,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"有線報左，建制派坐住一部白色既28 座離開中區警署"},{"pid":"bd93d62222c076202a54b273e552da03d9b907b0","tid":1207481,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4c0653fdb3bb35a861bbcc396b68fe9ad5431a","tid":1207481,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c7519fddca5df74dec8debd036c2d90c381216c","tid":1207481,"uid":4206,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"係，唔知駛去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一夠人夠票就宣布開會，殺個措手不及"},{"pid":"3ff87c9a1880a191741ba126ea0159eae12ff88c","tid":1207481,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8a87e6ee23f5173cde567816833b2795c45e5a0e","tid":1207481,"uid":177520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b647387d3f16cf3e7d34f203bf95cfc04462deb3